    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"background: var(--texture-grain); pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; opacity: 0.04; position: absolute; inset: 0\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px 48px 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100%;overflow:hidden;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: Playfair Display; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; color: #EDEEF5; margin: 0 0 12px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -0.015em; overflow-wrap: break-word\">What Nexus Ships</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);gap:6px;width:100%;flex:1;min-height:0;margin-top:8px;\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;min-height:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:10px;padding:4px 6px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#767CFF\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;color:#767CFF;\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M9 1v3M15 1v3M9 20v3M15 20v3M20 9h3M20 15h3M1 9h3M1 15h3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg></div>\n                <h3 style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 3px;line-height:1.25;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">Brief-to-Carousel</h3>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:8px;color:#CBCDD8;margin:0;line-height:1.35;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;flex:1;min-height:0;\">Write one paragraph about your product. Nexus generates the full emotional arc, picks slide types, and renders everything.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;min-height:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:10px;padding:4px 6px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83c\udfa8</div>\n                <h3 style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 3px;line-height:1.25;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">Theme Engine</h3>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:8px;color:#CBCDD8;margin:0;line-height:1.35;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;flex:1;min-height:0;\">Material Design tokens with tonal spot palettes. Every carousel gets a unique, consistent visual identity.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;min-height:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:10px;padding:4px 6px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#767CFF\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;color:#767CFF;\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"/><path d=\"m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"/><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4.5c1.39-1.4 4.5-2 4.5-2z\"/><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4.5-2c1.4-1.39 2-4.5 2-4.5z\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg></div>\n                <h3 style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 3px;line-height:1.25;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">CLI + MCP Server</h3>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:8px;color:#CBCDD8;margin:0;line-height:1.35;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;flex:1;min-height:0;\">Works as a standalone CLI or as an MCP tool any AI agent can call. No UI required.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;min-height:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:10px;padding:4px 6px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0;\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#767CFF\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;color:#767CFF;\"><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"4\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"14\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M3 20h18\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg></div>\n                <h3 style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:#EDEEF5;margin:0 0 3px;line-height:1.25;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;\">28 Campaign Presets</h3>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:8px;color:#CBCDD8;margin:0;line-height:1.35;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-word;flex:1;min-height:0;\">Pre-built emotional arcs for launches, thought leadership, data stories, and more \u2014 ready to fill and fire.</p>\n            </div></div></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
